then have the raid back off into one of the paths from the 2nd courtyard aways before u pull the last spider on the island&lt;spawning the single named plus the mini-spiders&gt;  have a druid or 2 at the bottom of the spider tunnel at 4way CY and pull the minispiders back to the last isle n kite them, as you kill the last spider and spawn the minis n Named.
<br />
then use the bards as listed n highsun them back to the raid..i did the highsunning when i did this event, hits maybe 40perc of time with HoS and a drum, just watch your range to the spiders as they hit a good distance and one stun/root proc and your smoke.
